title: Ep.16 Lakers Struggles, Cowboys, Chiefs Biggest Threat, Justin Jefferson, Score Predictions, and More.
description: Is Russell Westbrook the root of the Lakers problems? Are the Cowboys an actual Super Bowl contender this season? Who is the biggest threat to knock off the Chiefs? Justin Jefferson has the most receiving yards in NFL history in his first two seasons with 2 games left to play. Does he have what it takes to be the best WR ever?
